WEBVTT

00:11:59.880 --> 00:12:03.696
AG: There's evidence that in teams,
humility can be contagious.

00:12:03.720 --> 00:12:06.176
Sigal Barsade: The definition
of emotional contagion

00:12:06.200 --> 00:12:11.136
is when we are literally infected
with other people's emotions.

00:12:11.160 --> 00:12:13.216
AG: That's my colleague Sigal Barsade.

00:12:13.240 --> 00:12:15.896
She's a leading expert
on contagion and culture.

00:12:15.920 --> 00:12:20.856
SB: Emotional contagion
is something that I became interested in

00:12:20.880 --> 00:12:24.976
many, many years ago
when I was working with a colleague,

00:12:25.000 --> 00:12:28.216
"Meg" as a pseudonym,

00:12:28.240 --> 00:12:32.136
and I wasn't even reporting to her,
she was just working in my environment.